ZH: 我们需要一个投影仪来展示我们的演示文稿。
EN: We need a projector to display our presentation.

ZH: 他站在幕后控制投影仪的画面。
EN: He stood behind the scenes controlling the projected images.

ZH: 这个投影屏幕能够在白天也显示清晰的图像。
EN: This projection screen displays clear images even during the day.

ZH: 请将你的手放在我的手上，我将在投影上显示你的能力。
EN: Please put your hand on mine, and I will display your abilities on the projection.

ZH: 我们将在墙上投影一些旅游照片，让大家欣赏。
EN: We will project some travel photos on the wall for everyone to enjoy.

ZH: 投影仪上的电池用完了，你可以拿一个新的吗？
EN: The battery on the projector has run out, can you bring a new one?

ZH: 请注意不要触碰投影仪的镜头，以免损坏。
EN: Please be careful not to touch the lens of the projector, in order to avoid damage.

ZH: 我们需要一个能够对话并投影的智能助手。
EN: We need an intelligent assistant that can interact and project images.

ZH: 在影院里，他对投影机的音效感到震撼。
EN: In the cinema, he was amazed by the sound effects of the projector.

ZH: 请将这个USB插入投影仪的端口。
EN: Please insert this USB into the port of the projector.

ZH: 他迅速调整了投影仪的焦距，以获得更清晰的影像。
EN: He quickly adjusted the focus of the projector to get a clearer image.

ZH: 我们把幻灯片投影在墙上，方便大家查看。
EN: We projected the slides on the wall for everyone to view easily.

ZH: 教室里的投影墙上显示着数学公式。
EN: Mathematical formulas are displayed on the projection wall in the classroom.

