EN: The designer highlighted the projection feature of this phone as one of its biggest selling points.

ZH: 我们在会议室里放了一个投影仪，以便更好地讨论议题。
EN: We placed a projector in the meeting room for better discussion of the agenda.

ZH: 投影的画面上显示了一系列的数据报表。
EN: A series of data reports were displayed on the projected image.

ZH: 他用手机上的投影功能展示了他的摄影作品。
EN: He displayed his photography works using the projection feature on his phone.

